+## Constraints
+
+- Do not enumerate actual support survivors.
+- Do not derive the full exact projected ODEs.
+- Do not smuggle Tao-role or desired-channel labels into the raw object.
+- Do not count "could be useful after choosing the target channel" as
+  intrinsicity.
