+- `library/factual/tao-circuit-feature-ledger/INDEX.md`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- Do not start Step 2 enumeration in this report.
+- Do not derive the full phase evolution ledger.
+- Do not define delayed transfer by Tao-role labels alone.
+
