+   support class for this branch, including:
+   finite Fourier support vs finite helical support,
+   closure under recursive triad forcing,
+   spectator inclusion,
+   admissible enlargements,
+   smallest-first ordering,
+   and an escalation ladder?
+4. Which local materials best support quantitative delayed-transfer-facing
+   metrics tied to intrinsic clocks rather than narrative language, including:
+   transfer delay relative to turnover time,
+   transfer delay relative to viscous time,
+   spectator burden during the same window,
+   and a robustness standard?
