+### Ambient exact interaction scalar
+
+- `[INFERRED]` Before any packet or support aggregation, the cleanest exact
+  interaction datum attached to one Fourier triad `k = p + q` is
+
+  ```text
+  Gamma_{k,p,q}(u)
+    := -i * overline{u^(k)} · [ (q · u^(p)) P_k u^(q) ].
