+
+Return concrete findings, not just file paths, on these exact questions:
+
+1. Which local materials best support a very small family of candidate exact
+   phase/coherence objects built directly from exact Fourier or helical
+   interaction data, without desired-channel labels, packet sheets, or frozen
+   transfer annotations in the raw definition?
+2. Among locally supported candidates, which ones look most plausible as:
+   `intrinsic`,
+   `canonically representable but non-intrinsic`,
+   or
