+
+  ```text
+  Gamma_{k,p,q}(u)
+    = sum_(s_k,s_p,s_q) C_{k,p,q}^{s_k,s_p,s_q}
+      a_{s_p}(p) a_{s_q}(q) overline{a_{s_k}(k)}.
+  ```
+
+  So a candidate built from `Gamma_{k,p,q}` is already compatible with
